    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents at a very high level throughout. This is the kind of car that shows beautifully, with outstanding overall cosmetics, a very clean appearance, and the sort of careful preservation or restoration buyers hope to find. It is not being sold as a rough driver or a project; this is a truly top-tier car that should satisfy someone looking for a standout example to enjoy, show, and take pride in owning. Expect a car that looks, feels, and presents far above the average older vehicle on the market.",
