    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition car that appears to have been well cared for and should make a solid driver. It presents nicely inside and out, with a tidy interior, good overall finish, and the kind of normal age-related wear and small cosmetic imperfections you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle. It\u2019s an honest, appealing example for someone looking for a well-kept car they can enjoy without expecting showroom perfection.",
