    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for someone seeking dependable basic transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains an affordable way to get into a vehicle without stretching your budget. A practical choice for buyers who appreciate honest, no-nonsense value.",
